Class PhotoFeedbackList

    Class for representing details of a feedback given by the user. Feedback Lists are used by the clients to deliver feedback to the front-end. The feedback must always contain PhotoList with at least one Photo. The photos in the SimilarPhotoList and DissimilarPhotoList are similar and not similar to the photos listed in the ReferencePhotoList.

    Conditional Elements

    • similarMediaList
    • dissimilarMediaList
    At least one of the conditional elements must be present, and have valid content.
